  "detailed_description": "A bald man embarks on a punishing and difficult journey to get as high as possible. Climb up slowly or use your unique precision charge weapon to climb higher and faster with increased difficulty and greater risks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506000/extras/da2bfefdbf392999cb1d9a53f4dfd729.poster.avif?t=1691719971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506000/extras/da2bfefdbf392999cb1d9a53f4dfd729.webm?t=1691719971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2506000/extras/da2bfefdbf392999cb1d9a53f4dfd729.mp4?t=1691719971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The higher baldie gets, the more difficult and stressful it becomes. Especially if you choose hardcore mode...<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Large map with tons of unique areas<br></li><li> Precision gun mechanic<br></li><li> High degree of difficulty<br></li><li> Something special for those who reach the top<br></li><li> Fall down and lose your progress<br></li><li> You won't make it, just give up</li></ul>",
